24:48.472 --> 24:56.560
think about what you've learned, use the good 
intellect you have, Put the crows and toms down on

24:57.232 --> 24:59.374
your decision. Get that little crystal ball out. 
Look into it and make your decision. And that's

25:03.778 --> 25:10.103
been a real joy, a labor of love, that class over the 
years to see what's happened to people. Because

25:10.123 --> 25:16.869
every once in a while, Kay and you or someone will 
say, what's your track record in terms of people

25:10.123 --> 25:16.869
writing scenarios? I said, it's scary. It's 
phenomenal how they follow those scenarios.

25:23.115 --> 25:25.517
Because it's the first time in most of their 
careers They've never had to write down specific

25:25.801 --> 25:29.468
goals of where they're going in their life. So 
those are the three things.

25:37.142 --> 25:40.828
Most of them are out in the real world or are working 
on this campus. Now, some of them come right out of

25:40.849 --> 25:43.113
the bachelor's into the master's. We discourage 
that unless they're going into student affairs

25:43.133 --> 25:46.639
work. So I'll have some SAHI or student affairs 
people send.

