and more getting people coming in from out of state

25:55.703 --> 26:02.973
for our program. We have built kind of a reputation 
through our department. We've got some obviously

26:08.901 --> 26:16.932
internationally known people in our department, 
so we're beginning to attract people from out of

26:08.901 --> 26:16.932
state.

26:17.232 --> 26:22.960
We occasionally will attract one or two from 
Taiwan. Often we've had two from Russia who come

26:23.615 --> 26:31.530
here, and so we're beginning more and more to see. 
