26:59.484 --> 27:09.536
could be. Because I can remember the early PhD 
program, we had eight areas we were responsible

27:10.057 --> 27:15.724
for in education. And we had to try to master all 
eight of those areas in our written exams and

27:16.204 --> 27:21.350
everything else. And in many ways, of course, we 
