that was a waste. It was certainly a mental

27:29.898 --> 27:32.002
discipline. But I really believe that the rigor 
really has not changed. The technology has

27:39.113 --> 27:41.316
certainly changed a bit. And I'm experiencing 
that right now with our new APDGN system. And

27:47.205 --> 27:52.954
finding some limitations in that, knowing full 
well that eventually it's going to be a benefit.

