motivation leadership elements, and the futures 
class with the vision element, which is

28:00.848 --> 28:13.374
motivational. So those two courses, I have 
difficulty deciding between those two because I

28:13.394 --> 28:22.232
go into both those classes each night excited, 
pumped up, I try to get well prepared. I tell them

28:23.897 --> 28:27.942
that when they walk into that class, they better be 
ready, because I'm going to be ready. So those two I

28:27.962 --> 28:29.163
really enjoy. The third one, I don't have to really 
